                "caption": "Figure 1:(Left) A generated sample of the center of the city, where the four edges consist of green forest.\nOur model takes as input a segment map with text prompts for each segment and produces a world that corresponds to the input segment map (violet box) with high quality (blue and orange boxes).\n(Right) Two examples of generated worlds in large-scale.",
