            {
                "img": "https://arxiv.org/html/2605.00781/2605.00781v1/x2.png",
                "caption": "Figure 2:Visualization of the overall generation pipeline.\nFirst, we estimate the structured latent for a large world conditioned by a segmentation map and a text prompt for each segment using latent fusion (top).\nThen, we further upscale the resolution of the generated scene using the detail enhancer.\nDetail enhancer includes an MLP layer to incorporate condition latent and noise, as well as a flow Transformer (bottom).",
